      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Stefano Gemma</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:284px;\"><a href=\"https://www.g-sei.org/partite-8/#!gallery-sc1_2-8\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/7/73/Stefanogemma.jpg\" width=\"282\" height=\"212\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Stefanogemma.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Stefano Gemma at <a href=\"/CIPS_2001\" title=\"CIPS 2001\">CIPS 2001</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Stefano Gemma</b>,<br />\nan Italian IT consultant, owner of <i>L'Informatica di Gemma Stefano</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, and as computer chess programmer, \nfounding member of the <a href=\"/G_6\" title=\"G 6\">Gruppo Scacchi e Informatica</a>, the Italian Computer Chess Association, and author of the chess programs <a href=\"/Drago\" title=\"Drago\">Drago</a>, <a href=\"/Raffaela\" title=\"Raffaela\">Raffaela</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>,\n<a href=\"/Freccia\" title=\"Freccia\">Freccia</a>, <a href=\"/Satana\" title=\"Satana\">Satana</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, \nand <a href=\"/Sabrina\" title=\"Sabrina\">Sabrina</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1997_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1997 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefano_Gemma&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1997_...\">1997 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefano_Gemma&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1997 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/browse_frm/thread/48a30d15dae0840e\">What about far plyes precision?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, February 5, 1997</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=84735\">World computer chess championship</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 28, 1999</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefano_Gemma&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=125002\">Genetichal growing of chess-engines</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 18, 2000</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=125158\">Drago assembly sources available</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 2000</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=311652\">Raffaela 0.9</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 17, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=361885\">Best Algorithm Variation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 27, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=363895\">n/s again...</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 07, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Nodes_per_Second\" title=\"Nodes per Second\">Nodes per Second</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefano_Gemma&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=440629\">Raffaela 0.14.0 has beeen released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 07, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=29425\">Perft and mate</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 16, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Perft\" title=\"Perft\">Perft</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30008\">Overlapped Zobrist keys array</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 06, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Zobrist_Hashing\" title=\"Zobrist Hashing\">Zobrist Hashing</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefano_Gemma&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39873\">Assembly move generation in Freccia</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 26, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=41070\">New chess software announce: Satana</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 13, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=45532&amp;start=3\">Re: man-machine challenge part II</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 02, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=53552\">Just Take a Pebble...</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 03, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefano_Gemma&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55315\">Back to assembly</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 13, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Assembly\" title=\"Assembly\">Assembly</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56007\">Most common chess variant?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 15, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Games#ChessVariants\" title=\"Games\">Chess Variants</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57022\">* vs +</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 19, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57246\">Genetical tuning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 11, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a>, <a href=\"/Genetic_Programming\" title=\"Genetic Programming\">Genetic Programming</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61024\">AlfaGemma is back</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 03, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63785\">Freccia 0.0.2.5 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 21, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64167\">\"New\" chess engine: Sabrina</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 03, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64170\">AlfaGemma in Sabrina</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 03, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65616\">Sabrina 3.1.24 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 02, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66105\">Genetic optimization re-started</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 23, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66129\">Christmas gift</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 25, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Freccia\" title=\"Freccia\">Freccia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67969\">Sabrina 3.1.27 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 12, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=68063\">Drago is back</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 24, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=68286\">IGT 2018 - International G6 Tournament</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefano Gemma</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 23, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/IGT_2018\" title=\"IGT 2018\">IGT 2018</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefano_Gemma&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://it.linkedin.com/in/stefanogemma?trk=pub-pbmap\">Stefano Gemma - LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.linformatica.com/page_1.php\">L'Informatica di Gemma Stefano</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.linformatica.com/page_8.php\">Chess software for free, Original software made in Italy - author Stefano Gemma</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefano_Gemma&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Ed